# Conventional Commits for ollama-exporter
#
# Format: <type>(<scope>): <description>
#
# Types:
#   feat:     New feature (triggers minor version bump)
#   fix:      Bug fix (triggers patch version bump)
#   docs:     Documentation changes
#   style:    Code style changes (formatting, etc.)
#   refactor: Code refactoring
#   perf:     Performance improvements
#   test:     Adding or fixing tests
#   chore:    Maintenance tasks
#   ci:       CI/CD changes
#   build:    Build system changes
#
# BREAKING CHANGE: (triggers major version bump)
# Add "BREAKING CHANGE: <description>" in the footer
#
# Examples:
#   feat: add model temperature monitoring
#   fix: handle connection timeouts gracefully
#   docs: update Docker setup instructions
#   feat!: change API response format
#   BREAKING CHANGE: API now returns different structure
